<h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:22px;color:#1a1a2e;">Order Cancelled</h1>
<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
<p>Your order <strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong> has been cancelled.</p>

{{#if reason}}
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:24px 0;background-color:#fff3cd;border-radius:6px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:16px;">
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#856404;"><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
{{/if}}

<p>If a payment was made, the amount will be refunded to your payment method within 5–10 business days.</p>
<p style="color:#868e96;font-size:13px;">If you did not initiate this cancellation, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
